<div class='flex flex-col gap-4 lg:gap-6'>
    <div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
      <div class='grid gap-1'>
        <h1 class='font-heading text-2xl font-semibold dark:text-white'>Getting Started</h1>
        <p class='text-base text-muted-foreground'>Learn the basics of using our platform to build your startup.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'>
      <!-- Creating Your First Project -->
      <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-4'>
          <div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center'>
            {{lucide 'Plus' 'w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400'}}
          </div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground'>Creating Your First Project</h3>
        </div>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
          Start your entrepreneurial journey by creating your first project. This will be the foundation for all your startup activities.
        </p>
        <ol class='list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          <li>Click the "New Project" button in the sidebar</li>
          <li>Enter a descriptive name for your project</li>
          <li>Add a brief description of your idea</li>
          <li>Choose your industry category</li>
          <li>Click "Create Project" to get started</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigating the Dashboard -->
      <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-4'>
          <div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center'>
            {{lucide 'Compass' 'w-5 h-5 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400'}}
          </div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground'>Navigating the Dashboard</h3>
        </div>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
          Familiarize yourself with the main areas of our platform to make the most of your experience.
        </p>
        <ul class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          <li><strong>Sidebar:</strong> Access all main features and tools</li>
          <li><strong>Dashboard:</strong> Overview of your projects and progress</li>
          <li><strong>Ideas:</strong> Browse and generate new business ideas</li>
          <li><strong>AI Assistant:</strong> Get AI-powered recommendations</li>
          <li><strong>Portfolio:</strong> Track your business development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Setting Up Your Profile -->
      <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-4'>
          <div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 flex items-center justify-center'>
            {{lucide 'User' 'w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400'}}
          </div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground'>Setting Up Your Profile</h3>
        </div>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
          Complete your profile to personalize your experience and connect with other entrepreneurs.
        </p>
        <div class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          <p><strong>Basic Information:</strong> Add your name, bio, and location</p>
          <p><strong>Skills & Interests:</strong> Specify your expertise areas</p>
          <p><strong>Social Links:</strong> Connect your professional profiles</p>
          <p><strong>Preferences:</strong> Set your notification and privacy settings</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Understanding the Workspace -->
      <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-4'>
          <div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900 flex items-center justify-center'>
            {{lucide 'Briefcase' 'w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400'}}
          </div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground'>Understanding the Workspace</h3>
        </div>
        <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
          Learn how to organize and manage your startup development process effectively.
        </p>
        <div class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          <p><strong>Projects:</strong> Main containers for your startup ideas</p>
          <p><strong>Tasks:</strong> Break down projects into manageable steps</p>
          <p><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Work with team members and mentors</p>
          <p><strong>Resources:</strong> Access templates, guides, and tools</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

