              <span class='text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400'>4</span>
            </div>
            <span class='text-sm'>Build your business model</span>
          </div>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-3'>
            <div class='w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center'>
